# ============================================================================
# COMMENTS
# ============================================================================
# 
# NOTE: .env.example IS committed - it shows required variables without secrets
#
# Files SHOULD be committed:
#   - README.md, LICENSE, setup files
#   - Source code in src/, scripts/
#   - Configuration templates (.env.example)
#   - Dockerfile, docker-compose.yml
#   - GitHub workflow files (.github/workflows/)
#
# Files SHOULD NOT be committed:
#   - .env (use .env.example instead)
#   - Secrets, API keys, credentials
#   - venv/ virtual environment
#   - logs/, temp data
#   - __pycache__, .pytest_cache/
#
